<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=1042" title="Misty Morning"> Misty Morning</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p><img alt="mistyohio.jpg" src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/mistyohio.jpg" width="500" height="309" border="0" /></p>

	<p>The Ohio River was a rather steamy 44 compared with the 10 degree air temperature. Photo by Darlene Yarnetsky who survived 15 minutes on the riverfront before running back inside.</p>



 
<div class="line"></div>

<div class="smallcat">Posted in <a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?c=Madison">Madison</a></div>
