<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=1023" title="Beep, beep, beep"> Beep, beep, beep</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>I heard the backup alarms and scraping sounds loudly from our living room. I poked my head around the curtain and snapped some photos. We now have a mountain outside our front door.</p>

